Package: openmediavault-rsync-prometheus
Architecture: all
Depends: openmediavault (>= 7.0), curl
Description: Prometheus metrics for OpenMediaVault rsync jobs
 Wraps each rsync cronjob to push success/failure metrics and
 duration to a configurable Prometheus Pushgateway after every run.
